title: Tech wraps up day two of Texas Relays - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech wraps up day two of Texas Relays - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: AUSTIN, Texas – The Texas Tech track and field team completed day two of the Clyde Littlefield Texas Relays presented by Truist Thursday evening. Down the road in San Marcos, Konner Wood represented Tech at the Texas State Bobcat Invitational.
